    "Security and privacy.",
    "NDT should protect user privacy data and resist malicious attacks.",
    "Ensuring the fidelity of NDT to its physical counterparts demands rigorous security for safeguarding it against data manipulation and integrity breaches.",
    "With its significant role in managing personal data, privacy measures are indispensable to prevent leaks, particularly during data collection and processing.",
    "The network architecture must contemplate mechanisms for data security and privacy protection from the design phase."
